1 (6) (I) “QUALIFIED MARYLAND COMPANY” MEANS A COMPANY
2 THAT HAS MET THE CRITERIA IN SUBSECTION (C) OF THIS SECTION.
3 (II) “QUALIFIED MARYLAND COMPANY” DOES NOT INCLUDE A
4 COMPANY THAT IS OR HAS BEEN CERTIFIED AS A QUALIFIED MARYLAND
