10 (G) (1) (I) THERE IS AN ANGEL INVESTOR TAX CREDIT RESERVE
11 FUND WHICH IS A SPECIAL CONTINUING, NONLAPSING FUND THAT IS NOT SUBJECT
12 TO § 7–302 OF THE STATE FINANCE AND PROCUREMENT ARTICLE.
13 (II) THE MONEY IN THE RESERVE FUND SHALL BE INVESTED
