22 COMPANY ELIGIBLE FOR A TAX CREDIT.
23 (II) AN INITIAL TAX CREDIT CERTIFICATE ISSUED UNDER THIS
24 SUBSECTION SHALL STATE THE MAXIMUM AMOUNT OF TAX CREDIT FOR WHICH THE
25 QUALIFIED INVESTOR IS ELIGIBLE.
26 (III) 1. EXCEPT AS OTHERWISE PROVIDED IN THIS
27 SUBPARAGRAPH, FOR ANY FISCAL YEAR, THE SECRETARY MAY NOT ISSUE INITIAL
28 TAX CREDIT CERTIFICATES FOR CREDIT AMOUNTS IN THE AGGREGATE TOTALING
29 MORE THAN THE AMOUNT APPROPRIATED TO THE RESERVE FUND FOR THAT FISCAL
