31 REDUCED BY THE AMOUNT NEEDED TO PAY THE COSTS OF ADMINISTERING THE TAX
32 CREDIT PROGRAM UNDER THIS SECTION.
33 2. IF THE AGGREGATE CREDIT AMOUNTS UNDER INITIAL
34 TAX CREDIT CERTIFICATES ISSUED IN A FISCAL YEAR TOTAL LESS THAN THE

